@startuml title 《银纹秘境：彝饰守护者》游戏状态流转图

[*] --> MENU

MENU --> INTRO : 点击开始游戏
MENU --> [*] : 点击退出

INTRO --> PLAYING : 剧情引导结束

PLAYING --> DIALOGUE : 靠近NPC并按E
DIALOGUE --> PLAYING : 对话结束

PLAYING --> INVENTORY : 按I
INVENTORY --> PLAYING : 按I或Esc

PLAYING --> CODEX : 按G
CODEX --> PLAYING : 按G或Esc

PLAYING --> PATTERN_REALM : 与纹样点交互
PATTERN_REALM --> PLAYING : 完成或退出纹样小关卡

PLAYING --> REPAIR_MINIGAME : 与修复台交互且满足条件
REPAIR_MINIGAME --> PLAYING : 修复完成或退出

PLAYING --> ENDING : 节庆展示完成
ENDING --> MENU : 重新开始
ENDING --> [*] : 退出游戏

@enduml